{"tid":2512529,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Intel Ceo 稱歐盟需提供80億歐元補貼才能吸引Intel到歐洲設廠","createTime":"2021-05-01T19:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T02:16:08.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"025622ea82cb5a1600c8861af15739478d44b29d","tid":2512529,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T19:24:27.000Z","msg":"〔編譯魏國金／綜合報導〕在歐盟尋求降低對晶片進口的依賴之際，英特爾執行長季辛格接受美國網路媒體「政客」（Politico）歐洲版訪問表示，歐洲提供80億歐元（約2730億台幣）補貼，才會吸引英特爾在歐洲興建經晶圓廠，這是季辛格對歐洲建廠首度開出具體價碼。<br />\n<br />\n英特爾稍後對該報導採取距離，表示季辛格沒有提出具體數據，儘管他向歐盟領導人明確表示，必須進行相關投資，以確保半導體產業活絡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n季辛格上月30日在布魯塞爾與歐盟執委布勒東會面，此行之前，他才宣佈對於美國晶片生產投資200億美元。此外，季辛格也展望在歐洲某處興建晶圓廠。<br />\n<br />\n布勒東30日在與英特爾及三星高層會面前，先與與台積電歐洲子公司總經理默塞德（Maria Merced）舉行視訊會議，之後他推文形容，與季辛格進行「深入討論」，而與默塞德「良好交流」。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3518150\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3518150&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNqT%2B3fxaX50J59AF9IhbNpo%3D&h=a4df1cfc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3518150&h=08ce3101\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3518150</a>"},{"pid":"c07ab167830ebe2367e0ccad0d3e9c006dd75055","tid":2512529,"uid":360041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T23:03:18.000Z","msg":"(Not) you"},{"pid":"74649b8daeb09632526b1fba3235dae46590d438","tid":2512529,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:50:32.000Z","msg":"咪on9啦<br />\n你14nm用咗幾多年呀<br />\n點敢投資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf5961cfeeee3c8a54cef4122f25d76cc7901d9","tid":2512529,"uid":156913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:53:40.000Z","msg":"8B會唔會係平過叫台積電三星入EU?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9909e7063a7eb1326a4f80bb180280e9470edd